data.description: Presenting an enchanting three-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom townhome precisely 9 minutes 2.7 miles from Potomac Mills. This delightful residence spans three levels, inclusive of a basement and an attached garage, delivering an optimal blend of space and functionality. Seize the opportunity to acquire this exquisite 1 car garage townhouse with a kitchen boasting 42" cabinetry, a center island, stainless appliances, including a microwave, and adorned with granite countertops. Hardwood floors grace the main level, and the lower level offers versatility as a 3rd bedroom with a full adjacent bath or a recreational area. Experience the pleasure of entertaining on the deck overlooking the common area and tot-lot. The community features amenities such as a pool, tennis courts, walking trails, and a playground. Indulge in the convenience of nearby Stonebridge Potomac Town Center for shopping, including Wegmans and the Apple Store, as well as dining options like Uncle Julio's and Firebird. Offering additional choices. Easy access to I95 facilitates travel north to DC, Pentagon, and Ft Belvoir, or south to Quantico. The VRE is also conveniently nearby. Weekends can be enjoyed at Leesylvania State Park, just down Rt 1, providing opportunities for fishing, boating, hiking, and more. The sellers will arrange for professional cleaning services before move-out.
